summary: I can’t stop thinking about how vines exist in Marvel because I keep imaging this scene where Steve gets shot and Peter, in that...
body:
I can’t stop thinking about how vines exist in Marvel because I keep imaging this scene where Steve gets shot and Peter, in that instinctual way vine quoting comes out, goes: “How did you take down Captain America?”

and Steve goes in the same instinctual finishing a vine quote way: “Ve shot him in ze legs because his shield is ze size of a dinner plate. And he’s an idiot.”

And Peter’s immediately like well now I have to set fire to the whole internet.

summary: I’ve been seeing fan theories that Mr. Delmar could be Mary Jane’s father in Spider-man: Far from Home. I’d like for them to...
body: I’ve been seeing fan theories that Mr. Delmar could be Mary Jane’s father in Spider-man: Far from Home. I’d like for them to still keep MJ’s backstory as an abuse survivor though, so what if Delmar is actually her uncle instead and she lives with him and his wife, Anna, away from her abusive father?

summary:
MJ finds out Peter is Spiderman but Peter doesn’t know MJ knows he’s Spiderman
So she starts getting him funny presents
Like for...
body:
MJ finds out Peter is Spiderman but Peter doesn’t know MJ knows he’s Spiderman

So she starts getting him funny presents

Like for Christmas she gets him a shirt that says Spider-Man’s #1 fan!

And when he gets his first car she gets him a sticker that says “my other car is a web”

And one day after getting a Spiderman glow in the dark iPhone case he asks her

“Why do you always get me so much Spiderman stuff?”

And she just shrugs and says

“I think it’d be funny if the person with the most Spiderman march was Spiderman himself”

And she walks away

And Poor Pete is just standing there like :0
